DOC.brief_summary: Compare the efficacy of ABT-874 versus etanercept in subjects with moderate to severe plaque psoriasis
DOC.brief_title: Study Comparing the Efficacy and Safety of ABT-874 to Etanercept and Placebo in Subjects With Moderate to Severe Chronic Plaque Psoriasis
DOC.criteria: Diagnosis of Psoriasis for 6 MO BSA 10% PASI 12 or above PGA 3 or above Previous exposure to either etanercept or ABT874
